{
  "stem": "11144.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But their house, I think, was a little further out of the village.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was not in the middle of the village.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were probably paid by this Mr.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Goldman.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My mother probably paid, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But yes, they did take a risk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "No question about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So now, again, when there was fear or there was rumor that the Germans were approaching or coming, we all evacuated, left the house, and went to that-- to the in-ground-- in-ground shelter because that was in the closer proximity to their-- to their village or to their house.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was that shelter or any of the other shelters-- did the Germans or the Ukrainians ever raid any of them?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans didn't because, as I said, the Germans were afraid.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And somehow, I guess the villages that we stayed around-- they were more-- more Polish than Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And if there were a few Ukrainians there, they didn't-- you know, they-- they didn't want to be-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they wanted to be iso-- they didn't want to be isolated.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They wanted, really, to be integrated in the Polish community rather than showing that-- further east, where my husband comes from, there was more of the Ukrainian [UKRAINIAN] and [UKRAINIAN].",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they were-- they were merciless.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "While we were there already, we started-- not so much from the west.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't know, again-- I mean, I wasn't aware of what was happening in Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, we really didn't know what was going-- we had no idea what happened to our family.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't remember if my mother had gotten some news or not.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I-- I was not aware of what-- what was going on.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
